<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>13202</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20931</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我没疯。”阿拉丁对母亲说，“我只是爱上贝德拉公主了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20932</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30879</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“国王会怎么想？”泽巴问，“他怎么会把女儿交给你？谁敢这么请求他？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30880</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36490</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您。”阿拉丁回答说，“您去请求国王。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36491</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43490</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么？”泽巴大叫，“我？你觉得我也疯了吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43491</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48741</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果您不问，我就去死。”阿拉丁说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48742</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57009</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果我请求国王这么荒唐的事情，我们两个都得死！”泽巴大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57010</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62074</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他会觉得我们太大胆，杀死我们的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62075</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68830</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁想了一会儿，说：“国王是个好人。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68831</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74648</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“人们总是去他那里请求帮助。每个人都知道。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74649</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83312</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你说得对。”她同意道，“但是国王需要得到礼物，很好的礼物。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83312</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86898</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“因为他付出了时间和智慧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86899</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91059</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们没有什么好礼物送给他。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91060</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99737</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“妈妈，您说的没错。”阿拉丁说，“我们得带一个礼物去引起他的注意。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99738</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105211</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他脸色突然一变，脸上浮起了一个微笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105212</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111550</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“妈妈。”他说，“您忘记我从宝库中拿回来的珠宝了吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111551</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115223</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快，把家里最好的碗拿过来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115224</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122505</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>泽巴跑去了厨房，阿拉丁走到架子上的一个大罐前。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122506</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127686</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他从里面拿出了一个装满珠宝的皮包。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127687</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133870</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“给你，儿子。”泽巴边说边把碗递给阿拉丁。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133871</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137537</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁把珠宝倒进碗里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137538</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144416</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>美丽的宝石如此耀眼，以至于泽巴都睁不开眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144417</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149815</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这些都是世界上最大的珠宝。”阿拉丁说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149816</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157490</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您得把它们送给国王，然后告诉他您的儿子有多么想娶他女儿。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157491</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161850</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会照你说的做的，儿子。”泽巴说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161851</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169424</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她来到了一个宫殿大厅，大厅里挤满了想见国王的人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169425</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175156</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>泽巴很紧张，那些人看起来都很富有。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175157</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181292</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他们肯定都是些很重要的人！”她想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181293</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186556</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王最信任的首席大臣注视着一切。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186557</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193014</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看见泽巴走进大厅，坐在靠墙角落的位置。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193015</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201794</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那个女人是谁？她拿着什么？”他想，“她来找国王做什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201795</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211032</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>随着国王走进大厅，喇叭声响了起来，国王坐上了他的宝座。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211033</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216640</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每个人都站到了国王前面，请求他的帮助。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216641</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225116</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>泽巴一边看一边听。但是她太害怕了，不敢开口跟国王说话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225117</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229337</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当集会结束之后，她回了家。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229338</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234621</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每天，泽巴都去大厅，坐在相同的位置。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234622</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242356</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>许多天过去了，她还是不敢跟国王开口说她儿子的事情。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242357</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246322</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每晚，她都带着珠宝回家。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246323</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251354</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一天，国王向首席大臣倾过身子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251355</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258151</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那个每天都来的女人是谁？”他悄声说，“她想干什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258152</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>263692</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她不是什么重要的人。”首席大臣皱皱眉回答道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>263693</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>267793</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她可能只是想来抱怨她的邻居。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>267794</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>272243</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是国王对这个答案并不满意。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>272244</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>275835</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“明天，你把她带到我这儿来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>275836</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>283026</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天，泽巴还是坐在老位置，她一边看一边等。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>283027</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>287055</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然看到首席大臣指向她。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>287056</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>294864</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“站起来。”他命令道，“去见国王！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>